Titolo: Paganitzu

Anno: 1991

Descrizione: Paganitzu is a  puzzle video game created by Keith Schuler and published by Apogee Software for IBM PC compatibles in 1991. It is the sequel to Chagunitzu. The player controls Alabama "Al" Smith, who works his way through an ancient Aztec pyramid while solving Sokoban-like puzzles.
Paganitzu was published in three episodes: "Romancing the Rose","The Silver Dagger," and "Jewel of the Yucatan." The first was distributed as shareware. In 2015, it was re-released on Steam with Microsoft Windows and macOS support.

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: N/A
